    <item>
      <title>爱德华兹：美联储降息的问题是人们的生活是否会得到改善。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/edwards-fed-cut-question-is-will-people-see-improvement-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[劳工经济学家、彭博观点撰稿人凯瑟琳·爱德华兹 (Kathryn Edwards) 今天早些时候谈到了美联储四年多来首次降息，以及鲍威尔主席将如何努力在货币政策和政治之间保持明确的界限。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-18/edwards-fed-cut-question-is-will-people-see-improvement-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 18:55:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场参与者称美联储降息对信贷有利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/fed-cut-is-a-positive-for-credit-market-participants-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储周三宣布四年多来首次降息，将利率下调半个百分点，信贷衍生品利差随之收窄。]]></description>
